{"title_page": "KSI discography", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist          = [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]]\n| Image           = KSI performing 2019.png\n| Caption         = KSI performing in 2019.\n| Alt             = \n| Studio          = \n| Live            = \n| Video           = \n| Option name     = Collaborative albums\n| Option          = 1\n| Music videos    = 31\n| EP              = 4\n| Singles         = 28\n| 1Option name    = Promotional singles\n| 1Option         = 1 \n}}\nEnglish YouTube personality and rapper [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]] has released one collaboration album, four [[extended play]]s, 28 [[Single (music)|singles]] (including eight as a featured artist), and one [[promotional single]].\n\n==Albums==\n===Studio albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with selected details \n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:15em;\"| Album details\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Dissimulation ''\n|\n* Release date: May 2020<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d5_7wsSrnVo|title=I messed up... (6:30)|publisher=KSIOlajidebtHD V2|date=March 9, 2020|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n* Label: [[RBC Records|RBC]]\n* Formats: [[Music download|Digital download]], [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n|-\n|}\n\n===Collaborative albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of collaborative studio albums, with selected chart positions and details\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15em;\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"6\"| Peaks\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/54858/ksi-and-randolph/|title=KSI and Randolph: full Official Charts History|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=21 Apri